title: 200 Jailbreak Apps and Tweaks Compatible with iOS 10 – iOS 10.2
text:
Photo Tools AutoTouch 
These are all the jailbreak tweaks and apps that have been tested to work with iOS 10 – iOS 10.2. It is important that you avoid tweaks that don’t support iOS 10 as they may cause issues and force you to restore and lose your jailbreak. 
The list has been compiled from this Google Docs link , so we recommend that you also check this link regularly for newly added compatible tweaks.
